01:03:19.580 --> 01:03:20.580
Well, he has was the choirmaster at the school.
Because I was singing in the choir.

01:03:20.580 --> 01:03:21.580
And it was under the -- in those days we still
had steam trains

01:03:21.580 --> 01:03:22.580
traveling between Liverpool and Southport,
and that -- it was under one

01:03:22.580 --> 01:03:23.580
of the bridges that went over the train.
And then my sister ran back and told my mom

01:03:23.580 --> 01:03:24.580
about it.
Very embarrassing, cause years later having

01:03:24.580 --> 01:03:25.580
told this story, the Daily
Mail, of course, go and tracked down this

01:03:25.580 --> 01:03:26.580
ruddy chap.
No, no.

01:03:26.580 --> 01:03:27.580
This very nice chap who now runs a pub in
 -- somewhere in England.

01:03:27.580 --> 01:03:28.580
And he was insisted that we were not seven
and that we were older than

01:03:28.580 --> 01:03:29.580
that, but I am sure --

01:03:29.580 --> 01:03:30.580
&gt;&gt; He insists he was legal age.

01:03:30.580 --> 01:03:31.580
CHERIE BLAIR: No, no.
I think he insisted that we were about 9 or

01:03:31.580 --> 01:03:32.580
10, but he was wrong.

01:03:32.580 --> 01:03:33.580
&gt;&gt; Okay, well.
On that, do you have a question?

